<div class="WordSection1" style="layout-grid:15.6pt">

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">1.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="前言" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="0">Preface</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="癫痫是最常见的慢性神经系统疾病之一，病因不清、机制复杂、治疗困难[1]，并且癫痫发作导致严重的神经元凋亡，进一步加重中枢神经系统损害。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="1">Epilepsy is one of the most common chronic nervous system diseases. Its etiology is unclear, mechanism is complex, and treatment is difficult [1]. Moreover, epileptic seizures lead to serious neuronal apoptosis, further aggravating central nervous system damage.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="Ca2+对于调控细胞生存十分关键，可导致内质网应激介导的细胞凋亡[2]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="2">Ca2 + plays a key role in regulating cell survival, leading to endoplasmic reticulum stress-induced apoptosis [2].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="肌钙蛋白是主要的钙结合蛋白，在钙稳态中发挥重要作用[3]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="3">Troponin is the main calcium binding protein, which plays an important role in calcium homeostasis [3].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="内质网上的钙泵 SERCA，是钙稳态维持中唯一能降低胞内钙水平的部分，SERCA 通过将Ca2+从胞质转运到肌浆网或内质网中储存，使细胞内钙浓度维持在静息状态的低水平（约 100 nM）[4]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="4">SERCA, the calcium pump in the endoplasmic reticulum, is the only part that can reduce the intracellular calcium level in the maintenance of calcium homeostasis. SERCA keeps the intracellular calcium concentration at a low level (about 100 nm) in the resting state by transferring Ca2 + from the cytoplasm to the sarcoplasmic reticulum or endoplasmic reticulum for storage.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="本研究主要以 SERCA2（ATP2a2）基因及蛋白的表达为出发点，选取新生 24 h内的小鼠，通过分离培养原代海马神经元，按照 Sombati等人[5]的方法建立难治性癫痫细胞模型，利用western blot和实时荧光定量PCR（RT - PCR）技术检测难治性癫痫细胞模型中凋亡相关蛋白c-PARP[聚（" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="5">Based on the expression of SERCA2 (ATP2A2) gene and protein, the primary hippocampal neurons were isolated and cultured in 24-hour-old mice. According to Sombati et al. [5], the refractory epilepsy cell model was established. Western blot and real-time fluorescent quantitative PCR (RT-PCR) were used to detect c-parp [apoptosis related protein] in the refractory epilepsy cell model（</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="腺苷二磷酸核糖）聚合酶] 蛋白、ATP2a2（SERCA2）蛋白和 mRNA 表达的变化，并应用不同剂量的天麻素进行干预，探究 ATP2a2（SERCA2）在难治性癫痫发生过程中的作用及天麻素的抗癫痫机制。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="6">The changes of adenosine diphosphate ribose (ADP) polymerase] protein, ATP2A2 (SERCA2) protein and mRNA expression, and the intervention of different doses of gastrodin were used to explore the role of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) in the development of refractory epilepsy and the antiepileptic mechanism of gastrodin.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="材料与方法" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="7">Materials and methods</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.1</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="实验材料：新生24h内C57乳鼠，SPF级，由中国科学院生物物理研究所实验动物中心提供。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="8">Experimental materials: C57 suckling mice within 24 hours, SPF grade, provided by the experimental animal center of Institute of Biophysics, Chinese Academy of Sciences.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="ATP2a2/SERCA Antibody及Cleaved PARP Antibody (Asp214) (Mouse Specific)（9544S）由CST公司提供，Anti-NeuN 抗体（ab177487）由Abcam公司提供，Goat anti-Rabbit IgG(H+L) Secondary Antibody Fluor488（R37116）和Rabbit IgG(H+L) Secondary Antibody(31460) 由Thermo Scientific公司提供。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="9">ATP2A2 / SERCA anti and cleaned PARP anti (asp214) (mouse specific) (9544s) are provided by CST, anti NeuN antibody (ab177487) is provided by Abcam, and Goat anti rabbit IgG (H + L) secondary anti fluoro 488 (r37116) and rabbit IgG (H + L) secondary anti (31460) are provided by Thermo Scientific.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.2 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="实验方法" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="10">Experimental method</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.2.1 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="海马神经元的分离、原代培养及鉴定" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="11">Isolation, primary culture and identification of hippocampal neurons</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="取新生24 h内SPF级小鼠，75%酒精消毒，迅速断头取脑，于显微镜下迅速分离海马。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="12">The SPF mice were sterilized with 75% alcohol within 24 hours after birth. The brain was cut off and the hippocampus was separated under microscope.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将分离出的海马组织转移至装有 1 mL 0.25%胰酶的 35 mm小皿中，剪碎成约 1 mm3 的小块，置于 37 ℃培养箱 20 min，在超净台中将其吸取至 15 mL 离心管，加入至少 5 mL 的 Plating media，1000 r/min离心5min，吸弃上清液。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="13">Transfer the isolated hippocampal tissue to a 35 mm dish containing 1 ml of 0.25% pancreatin, cut it into small pieces of about 1 mm3, place it in a 37 ℃ incubator for 20 minutes, draw it to a 15 ml centrifuge tube in a super clean platform, add at least 5 ml of plating media, centrifugate it at 1000 R / min for 5 minutes, and suck up and discard the supernatant.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="再加2 mL Plating media轻柔吹打约20次重悬，40μm细胞筛过滤。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="14">Add 2 ml of plating media and gently blow it for 20 times for heavy suspension, and filter it with 40 μ M cell sieve.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="取10μL细胞悬液与10μL台盼蓝液混合均匀后，取10μL混合液细胞计数仪计数。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="15">Take 10 μ L cell suspension and 10 μ l trypan blue solution and mix them evenly, then take 10 μ l mixed solution cell counter to count.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将细胞悬液稀释成 2×10/mL 细胞数准备种植。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="16">The cell suspension was diluted to 2 × 10 / ml cells for planting.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="六孔板及 confocal 小皿预先经过 Poly-L-lysine 处理30 min并用无菌水清洗 3 次后晾干。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="17">The six hole plate and confical dish were pretreated with poly-L-lysine for 30 min and washed with sterile water for 3 times before drying.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="每孔2 mL种植六孔板；每孔200μL种植于confocal小皿并于40min后加Plating media至2 mL。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="18">Six hole plate was planted with 2 ml per hole; 200 μ l per hole was planted in a confical dish and platting media was added to 2 ml after 40 min.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将孔板及小皿置于37℃、5%CO2细胞培养箱内，培养4-10 h后，每孔换液为2ml Culture media后继续培养，之后每3天半量换液 1次。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="19">The plates and plates were placed in a 37 ℃ 5% CO2 cell incubator. After 4-10 hours of culture, the cells were changed into 2ml culture media for each pore, and then continued to be cultured. After that, the cells were changed once every three and a half days.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养至第5时通过免疫荧光鉴定神经元，用神经元特异性标志物 NeuN 抗体标记神经元。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="20">The neurons were identified by immunofluorescence and labeled by NeuN antibody.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="免疫荧光结果判定标准及方法：在激光共聚焦成像系统中观察并拍摄照片，在40倍显微镜下，随意选择视野，计算每个视野中阳性细胞率，重复3次，计算其平均值作为神经元纯度。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="21">Criteria and methods for determination of immunofluorescence results: observe and take photos in the laser confocal imaging system, select the field of vision randomly under the 40 times microscope, calculate the positive cell rate in each field, repeat 3 times, and calculate the average value as the neuron purity.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.2.2 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="建立难治性癫痫细胞模型及分组" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="22">Establishment of cell model and grouping of intractable epilepsy</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="难治性癫痫细胞模型参考 Sombati等人的方法建立[39]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="23">The cell model of intractable epilepsy was established by Sombati et al [39].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将六孔板中培养至第 7 天的海马神经元随机分组为正常对照组（C）、模型组（M）、模型+1μM 天麻素组（G1）、模型+10μM天麻素组（G2）、模型+100μM天麻素组（G3），模型+1 mM天麻素组（G4）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="24">The hippocampal neurons cultured in the six pore plate were randomly divided into normal control group (c), model group (m), model + 1 μ m gastrodin group (G1), model + 10 μ m gastrodin group (G2), model + 100 μ m gastrodin group (G3), model + 1 mm gastrodin group (G4).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="正常对照组换液为正常细胞外液培养3 h 后恢复为 2 mL Culture media培养，模型组换液为无镁细胞外液培养3 h后恢复为2mL Culture media培养，各浓度天麻素组换液为无镁细胞外液培养3 h后每孔恢复为已分别加入 1μM、10μM、100μM、1mM 浓度天麻素的 Culture media，将六孔板放回" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="25">The normal control group was cultured in normal extracellular solution for 3 hours and then returned to 2 ml culture media culture. The model group was cultured in magnesium free extracellular solution for 3 hours and then returned to 2 ml culture media culture. Each cell in each concentration of gastrodin group was cultured in magnesium free extracellular solution for 3 hours and then returned to culture media with 1 μ m, 10 μ m, 100 μ m and 1 mM concentration of gastrodin respectively. The six hole plate was put back</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养箱继续培养 24 h。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="26">The culture continued for 24 hours.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="2.2.3 ATP2a2（SERCA2）及 c-PARP 蛋白表达的检测" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="27">2.2.3 detection of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) and c-parp protein expression</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.2.3.1 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="提取细胞总蛋白及测定总蛋白浓度" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="28">Extraction of total protein and determination of total protein concentration</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将建模后继续培养24h的各组神经元的六孔板从培养箱中拿出置于冰上，吸走各孔培养基，按 1:100 比例添加 PI 及 PMSF 至 RIPA（弱）裂解液中，将细胞碎片和裂解液的混合液用移液枪吸取至 1.5 mL EP管中，冰上裂解 20 min，预冷的 4℃离心机12000 r/min 离心 10 min，小心将上" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="29">Take out the six pore plates of each group of neurons which continue to be cultured for 24 hours after modeling from the incubator and put them on ice, suck out each pore medium, add PI and PMSF to Ripa (weak) lysate in the proportion of 1:100, draw the mixture of cell fragments and lysate into 1.5 ml EP tube with a pipette gun, split it on ice for 20 minutes, centrifugate it for 10 minutes with a precooled 4 ℃ centrifuge of 12000 R / min, and carefully put it on</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="清吸取至新的 EP 管中，按照 Pierce™ BCA Protein Assay Kit（23227）试剂盒说明书进行测浓度操作，计算蛋白样品的浓度。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="30">Pipette the albumin into the new EP tube, measure the concentration according to the instructions of Pierce? BCA protein assay kit (23227) kit, and calculate the concentration of protein sample.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="2.2.3.2 Western blot" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="31">2.2.3.2 Western blot</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="按标准分别将厚、薄玻璃板对齐垂直卡于制胶架上，灌胶配制蛋白胶。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="32">According to the standard, the thick and thin glass plates are aligned and vertically clamped on the glue making frame, and then filled with glue to prepare protein glue.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将配制好的蛋白胶夹紧放入电泳槽，根据测定的蛋白浓度，将每组样品各取出30μg 量至1.5 mL EP管，加入6×SDS上样缓冲液至终浓度为1×，混合均匀，100℃金属浴 5 min 使蛋白变性。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="33">Clamp the prepared protein glue into the electrophoresis tank, take out 30 μ g of each group of samples to 1.5ml EP tube according to the measured protein concentration, add 6 × SDS sample buffer solution to the final concentration of 1 × and mix evenly, and denature the protein in 100 ℃ metal bath for 5 minutes.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="用移液枪依次吸取蛋白 ladder 及蛋白样品，将枪头伸入加样孔中缓慢加入样品。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="34">Pipette the protein ladder and protein sample in turn with the pipette gun, then extend the gun head into the sample hole and slowly add the sample.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="电压60V恒压电泳至浓缩胶跑完、ladder分开；加压为110V，恒压跑至溴酚蓝即将跑出，终止电泳，开始转膜，200 mA恒流转2h。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="35">After 60 V constant pressure electrophoresis, the concentrated gel runs to the end, and the ladder is separated; when the pressure is 110 V, the bromophenol blue runs to the end, the electrophoresis is stopped, and the membrane is transferred, and the 200 Ma constant flow is 2 h.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="转完膜后，将膜用镊子夹取至含有 5%脱脂牛奶（用TBST配制）的平皿中，室温摇床上低速封闭1 h。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="36">After rotating the membrane, clamp the membrane with tweezers to a plate containing 5% skimmed milk (prepared with tbst), and close it at low speed on a shaker at room temperature for 1 h.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="用镊子将膜夹至一抗体液中，放于4 ℃层析柜中脱色摇床上低速孵育过夜；倒掉抗体液，加入TBST涮洗1次，再室温用 TBST脱色摇床中高速洗 4 次，每次 10 min。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="37">Clamp the membrane into an antibody solution with tweezers, and put it into a decolorizing shaker at 4 ℃ for incubation overnight at low speed; pour out the antibody solution, add tbst for washing once, and then use tbst decolorizing shaker at room temperature for washing four times at high speed for 10 min each time.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="同样，将二抗用 5%脱脂奶粉稀释成合适浓度，倒入抗体孵育盒中，室温脱色摇床低速孵育1-2h；倒掉抗体液，加入TBST涮洗1次，再室温用TBST脱色摇床中高速洗4次，每次10min。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="38">Similarly, dilute the second antibody with 5% skimmed milk powder to a proper concentration, pour it into the antibody incubator, and incubate it in a decolorizing shaker at room temperature for 1-2h at a low speed; pour out the antibody solution, add tbst to rinse it once, and then wash it in a decolorizing shaker at room temperature for 4 times at a high speed for 10min each time.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将膜夹起，放置仪器暗盒平台上，滴加已1:1现混匀的发光液，关上暗盒，开始曝光。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="39">Clamp up the film, place it on the dark box platform of the instrument, add 1:1 mixed luminous liquid, close the dark box and start exposure.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="完成后，选择条带曝光度合适的图片保存。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="40">When finished, select a picture with appropriate stripe exposure to save.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="用Image J软件分析比较条带的灰度值。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="41">Image J software is used to analyze and compare the gray value of the strip.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="2.2.4 ATP2a2（SERCA2）及内参β- actin mRNA 表达的检测" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="42">2.2.4 detection of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) and β - actin mRNA expression</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="将建模后继续培养 24 h 的各组神经元的六孔板从培养箱中拿出，按照说明书提取各组神经元总的 RNA，将所得的 RNA 产物保存于-80 ℃冰箱。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="43">Take out the six pore plates of each group of neurons that continue to be cultured for 24 hours after modeling from the incubator, extract the total RNA of each group of neurons according to the instructions, and store the RNA products in the refrigerator of - 80 ℃.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="同时取样进行RNA完整性和RNA纯度检测检测。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="44">At the same time, RNA integrity and purity were detected.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="参照 Invitrogen 公司的 SuperScript™ III First-Strand Synthesis System for RTPCR 试剂盒（1701598）说明书进行cDNA合成。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="45">Refer to the instruction manual of superscript? III first strand synthesis system for RTPCR Kit (1701598) of Invitrogen company for cDNA synthesis.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="根据鼠 ATP2a2 mRNA及内参β-actin基因的全序列，用SnapGene软件进行引物设计，引物序列：ATP2a2：Forward: 5'- GTTGGTGACAAAGTTCCTGC -3'，Reverse: 5'-TGTCTTGATTAACAGCTCGGG-3'；β- actin：Forward: 5'- ACCTTCTACAATGAGCTGCG -3'，Reverse: 5'- CTGGATGGCTACGTACATGG -3'。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="46">According to the complete sequence of rat ATP2A2 mRNA and internal reference β - actin gene, the primers were designed by snapgene software. The primer sequence was ATP2A2: forward: 5 '- gttggtgaaagttcctggc-3', reverse: 5 '- tgtcttgataagctcgggg-3'; β - actin: forward: 5 '- accttacatgtgtgtgtgcg-3', reverse: 5 '- ctggaggctactagtaggg-3'.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="引物均由北京奥科鼎盛生物科技有限公司合成。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="47">All primers were synthesized by Beijing Aoke Dingsheng Biotechnology Co., Ltd.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="实时荧光定量 PCR（RT-PCR）检测各组神经元中ATP2a2和β- actin基因的相对表达水平。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="48">The relative expression levels of ATP2A2 and β - actin genes were detected by real-time fluorescence quantitative PCR (RT-PCR).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">2.2.5 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="统计学数据处理" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="49">Statistical data processing</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="数据处理分析应用方差分析，检验方差齐性后，采用 LSD-t检验比较各组两两之间的差异，样本均数采用 t 检验，P<0.05 即认为差异具有统计学意义。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="50">Variance analysis was used in data processing analysis. After the homogeneity of variance was tested, LSD-t test was used to compare the differences between the two groups. T test was used for sample mean, P &lt; 0.05, which means that the differences are statistically significant.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">3.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="结果" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="51">Result</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">3.1 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="倒置相差显微镜下体外培养海马神经元的形态学观察" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="52">Morphological observation of cultured hippocampal neurons under inverted phase contrast microscope</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="刚分离种植的海马神经元为圆形，透亮，无突起，呈单细胞悬浮状态（Figure 1（a））；4-6h后，绝大部分海马神经元可以良好贴壁，少数神经元可有 1-2个小突起长出。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="53">After 4-6h, most of the hippocampal neurons could adhere to the wall well, and a few neurons could have 1-2 small processes.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="种植6-10h后 Plating media全部换液为Culture media。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="54">After 6-10 hours of planting, plating media was replaced with culture media.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养第3天，贴壁的海马神经元伸长出粗细不均的数个突起，胞体透亮，呈梭形、三角形等，相邻的神经元之间可有稀疏网络连接（Figure1（b））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="55">On the third day of culture, the adherent hippocampal neurons elongated several processes with uneven thickness, the cell body was transparent, fusiform and triangular, and the adjacent neurons could have sparse network connection (Figure 1 (b)).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养至第5天的海马神经元，生长状态良好，立体感和折光性明显，胞体增大，突起延长交织成网（Figure1 （c））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="56">The hippocampal neurons cultured to the 5th day were in good growth condition, with obvious stereopsis and refraction, increased cell body and elongated protuberances interwoven into a net (Figure 1 (c)).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养第7天的海马神经元，胞体增大饱满，有明显的光晕；神经元突起变多，轴突细长，神经元之间突起相互交织，形成稠密复杂但分布均匀的神经网络（Figure 1（d））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="57">On the 7th day of culture, the hippocampal neurons were enlarged and plump with obvious halo; the neurites became more and more, the axons were slender, and the neurites were interwoven with each other, forming a dense and complex but evenly distributed neural network (Figure 1 (d)).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%"><img width="553" height="407" id="图片 4" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image001.jpg"></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="图 1 海马神经元生长不同天数的形态变化" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="58">Figure 1 morphological changes of hippocampal neurons in different days</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="Figure 1 Morphological changes of hippocampal neurons in different days." class="translated-span" data-span-idx="59">Figure 1 Morphological changes of hippocampal neurons in different days.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">3.2 </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="难治性癫痫细胞模型及加药组细胞形态学变化" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="60">Cell model of intractable epilepsy and cell morphological changes in the treated group</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="培养第7天，模型组换液为无镁细胞外液处理3h建立难治性癫痫细胞模型，正常对照组换液为正常细胞外液培养3h。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="61">On the 7th day of culture, the model group was treated with magnesium free extracellular solution for 3 hours to establish the refractory epilepsy cell model, and the normal control group was treated with normal extracellular solution for 3 hours.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="建模24h后（即培养的第8天），正常对照组（C）神经元胞体饱满，光晕清晰，突起丰富且交织成复杂但分布均匀有序的神经网络（Figure2（a））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="62">After 24 hours of modeling (i.e. the 8th day of Culture), the normal control group (c) had full cell body, clear halo, rich protuberances and interwoven into a complex but well distributed neural network (Figure 2 (a)).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="在建模24h后，模型组（M）的海马神经元出现迁移、融合，有死亡的神经元漂浮，神经网格变得杂乱且分布不均（Figure 2（b））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="63">After 24 hours of modeling, the hippocampal neurons in model group (m) migrated and fused, and dead neurons floated, and the neural grid became disordered and unevenly distributed (Figure 2 (b)).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="建模3 h 换液为正常Culture media后，加入终浓度分别为1μM、10μM、100 μM、1mM的天麻素，神经元状态有不同程度的好转，融合的神经元不同程度减少，神经网格分布比较均匀，100μM天麻素组（M+G）即可见明显效果（Figure 2（c））。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="64">After 3 hours of modeling and changing to normal culture media, the final concentration of 1 μ m, 10 μ m, 100 μ m and 1mm gastrodin were added respectively. The state of neurons improved in different degrees, the number of fused neurons decreased in different degrees, and the distribution of neural grid was relatively uniform. The effect of 100 μ m gastrodin group (M + G) was significant (Figure 2 (c)).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%"><img width="554" height="181" id="图片 3" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image002.jpg"></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
宋体" data-src-str="图 2 难治性癫痫细胞模型组和天麻素处理组神经元形态学变化" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="65">Figure 2 morphological changes of neurons in refractory epilepsy cell model group and gastrodin treated group</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="Figure 3 Morphological changes of neurons in cell model of epilepsy Group and gastrodin group" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="66">Figure 3 Morphological changes of neurons in cell model of epilepsy Group and gastrodin group</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="3.3 ATP2a2（SERCA2）及 c-PARP 蛋白表达的检测" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="67">3.3 detection of protein expression of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) and c-parp</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="（1）建模24h后，模型组（M）较正常对照组（C）ATP2a2 蛋白表达降低，而凋亡指标c-PARP蛋白增高；相比较于模型组，各浓度天麻素组（G1、G2、G3、G4）ATP2A2 蛋白表达均有上调，而凋亡水平有不同程度的降低（Figure 3-1）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="68">(1) 24 hours after modeling, the expression of ATP2A2 protein in the model group (m) was lower than that in the normal control group (c), while the apoptotic index c-parp protein was higher; compared with the model group, the expression of ATP2A2 protein in each concentration of gastrodin group (G1, G2, G3, G4) was up-regulated, while the apoptotic level was reduced in varying degrees (Figure 3-1).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%"><img width="548" height="264" id="图片 2" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image003.png"></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="图 3-1 ATP2a2（SERCA2）及 c-PARP 蛋白表达" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="69">Figure 3-1 protein expression of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) and c-parp</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="Figure 3-1 Expression of ATP2a2（SERCA2）and c-PARP" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="70">Figure 3-1 Expression of ATP2a2（SERCA2）and c-PARP</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
宋体" data-src-str="根据形态学表现及凋亡指标 c-PARP 蛋白表达水平，选择应用明显缓解凋亡、神经元状态最好的天麻素浓度，即100uM天麻素。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="71">According to the morphological features and expression level of c-parp protein, the best concentration of gastrodin, i.e. 100 um gastrodin, was selected to alleviate apoptosis and neuron state.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:
宋体" data-src-str="相比较于模型组（M），100 μM天麻素组（G）能显著上调 ATP2a2 蛋白表达水平，而降低 c-PARP（凋亡）水平（Figure 3-2-1）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="72">Compared with the model group (m), the 100 μ m gastrodin group (g) can significantly up regulate the expression level of ATP2A2 protein and reduce the c-parp (apoptosis) level (Figure 3-2-1).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%"><img width="554" height="495" id="图片 1" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image004.jpg"></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="图 3-2 ATP2a2（SERCA2）及 c-PARP 蛋白表达" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="73">Figure 3-2 protein expression of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) and c-parp</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt" data-src-str="Figure 3-2 Expression of ATP2a2（SERCA2）and c-PARP" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="74">Figure 3-2 Expression of ATP2a2（SERCA2）and c-PARP</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt" data-src-str="#表示与对照组相比，P<0.05，差别具有统计学意义；*表示与模型组相比，P<0.05，差别具有统计学意义。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="75">#Compared with the control group, P &lt; 0.05, the difference was statistically significant; * compared with the model group, P &lt; 0.05, the difference was statistically significant.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="3.4 ATP2a2 的 mRNA 表达的检测" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="76">3.4 detection of ATP2A2 mRNA expression</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="建模 24 h 后，各组 ATP2a2 的 mRNA 表达的变化；与正常对照组（C）相比较，模型组（M）ATP2a2 mRNA表达量显著降低（P<0.05）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="77">After 24 hours of modeling, the expression of ATP2A2 mRNA in each group was significantly lower than that in the normal control group (c) (P &lt; 0.05).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="与模型组（M）相比较，100 μM 天麻素组（G）能显著上调 ATP2a2 mRNA 表达，差异具有统计学意义（P<0.05）（见 Table 1）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="78">Compared with the model group (m), 100 μ m gastrodin group (g) can significantly up regulate the expression of ATP2A2 mRNA, the difference is statistically significant (P &lt; 0.05) (see Table 1).</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="表1 各组荧光定量 PCR 检测 ATP2a2 mRNA 结果" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="79">Table 1 results of ATP2A2 mRNA detected by FQ-PCR in each group</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="position:absolute;z-index:251656704;left:0px;margin-left:-1px;
margin-top:26px;width:559px;height:8px"><img width="559" height="8" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image005.png"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="Table 1 RT - PCR results of ATP2a2 mRNA of different groups" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="80">Table 1 RT - PCR results of ATP2a2 mRNA of different groups</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="position:absolute;z-index:251657728;left:0px;margin-left:-1px;
margin-top:26px;width:559px;height:8px"><img width="559" height="8" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image005.png"></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="组别               例数        相对表达量" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="81">Relative expression of group cases</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:66.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="正常对照组（C 组）     3          1.006386" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="82">Control group (Group C) 3 1.006386</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:96.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="模型组（M）      3          0.595942#" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="83">Model group (m) 3 0.595942#</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span style="position:absolute;
z-index:251658752;left:0px;margin-left:-5px;margin-top:29px;width:559px;
height:8px"><img width="559" height="8" src="https://fanyi-doc.baidu.com/doctrans/api/getmultimedia?fileToken=2823a53aae8fe7bc83045b4a91532cb1&amp;name=image005.png"></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="模型+100uM 天麻素组（G 组）      3          0.995774*" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="84">Model + 100um gastrodin group (group G) 30.995774*</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%" data-src-str="#表示与对照组相比，P<0.05，差别具有统计学意义；*表示与模型组相比，P<0.05，差别具有统计学意义" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="85">#Compared with the control group, P &lt; 0.05, the difference is statistically significant; * compared with the model group, P &lt; 0.05, the difference is statistically significant</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">4.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="讨论" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="86">discuss</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="癫痫，是脑部神经元高度同步化异常放电的一种临床综合征，主要病理特征表现为海马硬化和苔藓纤维出芽，其临床表现特点：具有发作性、刻板性、短暂性和重复性；不同位置神经元的异常放电可致不同的发作形式，可表现为运动、行为、感觉、精神、意识和自" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="87">Epilepsy is a clinical syndrome of highly synchronized abnormal discharge of neurons in the brain. Its main pathological features are hippocampal sclerosis and mossy fiber sprouting. Its clinical features are paroxysmal, stereotyped, transient and repetitive. Abnormal discharge of neurons at different locations can cause different seizure forms, which can be manifested as movement, behavior, sensation, spirit, consciousness and self</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="主神经功能障碍或者均有之。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="88">Main nerve dysfunction or both.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="癫痫的病因不清，发病机制复杂，同时在癫痫发作过程中存在神经元的凋亡，神经元凋亡与癫痫发作形成一个正反馈，使癫痫的治疗更加困难。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="89">The etiology of epilepsy is unclear and the pathogenesis is complex. At the same time, there is apoptosis of neurons in the process of seizure. Neuron apoptosis and seizure form a positive feedback, which makes the treatment of epilepsy more difficult.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="因此如何有效控制癫痫发作同时抑制神经元凋亡是癫痫治疗的主要探索方向。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="90">Therefore, how to effectively control seizures and inhibit neuronal apoptosis is the main direction of epilepsy treatment.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="而Ca2+是重要的信号分子，参与调控细胞的很多生理功能，如细胞增殖、信号转导、肌肉收缩、转录、蛋白的折叠以及凋亡等。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="91">Ca2 + is an important signal molecule involved in regulating many physiological functions of cells, such as cell proliferation, signal transduction, muscle contraction, transcription, protein folding and apoptosis.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="而不少研究表明 Ca2+与癫痫发病密不可分，并且对于调控细胞生存十分关键的 Ca2+，其失调（如动作电位启动时，胞内 Ca2+水平的急剧升高（极化）钙超载）可激活内质网应激，从而启动细胞凋亡，最终导致细胞死亡[2]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="92">However, many studies have shown that Ca2 + is closely related to epilepsy, and Ca2 + is very important for the regulation of cell survival. Its disorder (such as the sharp increase of intracellular Ca2 + level (polarization) calcium overload when action potential is activated) can activate endoplasmic reticulum stress, thus initiating cell apoptosis, and ultimately leading to cell death [2].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="近年来，随着相关研究的进展迅速，已有针对 Ca2+的相关药物投入临床应用，如可以调节神经兴奋性的电压依赖性钙通道，其抑制剂在临床上已被用应用于癫痫治疗。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="93">In recent years, with the rapid development of related research, there have been related drugs for Ca2 + put into clinical application, such as voltage-dependent calcium channel, which can regulate nerve excitability, and its inhibitors have been used in epilepsy treatment.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="内质网上的钙泵 SERCA，是钙稳态维持中唯一能降低胞内钙水平的部分，SERCA 通过将Ca2+从胞质转运到肌浆网或内质网中储存，使细胞内钙浓度维持在静息状态的低水平（约 100 nM）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="94">SERCA, the calcium pump in the endoplasmic reticulum, is the only part that can reduce the intracellular calcium level in the maintenance of calcium homeostasis. SERCA keeps the intracellular calcium concentration at a low level (about 100 nm) in the resting state by transporting Ca2 + from the cytoplasm to the sarcoplasmic reticulum or endoplasmic reticulum for storage.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="天麻素作为一个传统抗癫痫中药天麻重要的单体成份，是否能够在控制癫痫的同时并且抗凋亡作用，目前未见报道，因此我们拟通过建立难治性癫痫细胞模型，利用western blot和实时荧光定量PCR（RT - PCR）技术检测难治性癫痫细胞模型中凋亡相关蛋白c-PARP[聚（腺苷二" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="95">As an important monomer of traditional Chinese medicine Gastrodia elata, it has not been reported whether gastrodin can control epilepsy and anti apoptotic effect at the same time. Therefore, we intend to use Western blot and real-time fluorescence quantitative PCR (RT-PCR) technology to detect apoptosis related protein c-parp [poly (adenosine diphenyl) in intractable epilepsy cell model by establishing intractable epilepsy cell model</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="磷酸核糖）聚合酶] 蛋白、ATP2a2（SERCA2）蛋白和 mRNA 表达的变化，并应用不同剂量的天麻素进行干预，探究 ATP2a2（SERCA2）在难治性癫痫发生过程中的作用及天麻素的抗癫痫机制。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="96">In order to explore the role of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) in the development of refractory epilepsy and the antiepileptic mechanism of gastrodin, we used different doses of gastrodin to intervene.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="癫痫的实验模型很多，包括细胞模型、脑片模型和动物模型等。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="97">There are many experimental models of epilepsy, including cell model, brain slice model and animal model.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="细胞模型，由于不受体内复杂因素的干扰，实验重复性好，和相对较丰富的获取来源，在癫痫相关的研究中独具优势。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="98">Cell model, which is not interfered by complex factors in vivo, has good experimental repeatability and relatively rich sources of acquisition, and has unique advantages in epilepsy related research.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="Sombati等人通过无镁细胞外液培养海马神经元3h 构建的难治性癫痫细胞模型，即使建模后恢复正常条件培养，2- 3周后仍能检测到神经元的异常放电，因此该模型十分稳定、可靠且持续性好[6, 7]。 " class="translated-span" data-span-idx="99">Sombati et al. Established a refractory epileptic cell model by culturing hippocampal neurons in magnesium free extracellular solution for 3 hours. Even if the normal condition culture is restored after modeling, abnormal discharge of neurons can be detected after 2-3 weeks, so the model is very stable, reliable and has good sustainability [6, 7].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="Jun Xiang 和 Fang Wen利用体外培养的海马神经元构建难治性癫痫细胞模型，发现 FOXD3 基因抑制了SCN2A基因转录，而敲降 FOXD3后 SCN2A基因表达可以增加，减少了难治性癫痫细胞模型中无镁细胞外液对神经元造成的损伤[8]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="100">Jun Xiang and Fang Wen used cultured hippocampal neurons to construct a refractory epilepsy cell model. They found that FoxD3 gene inhibited the transcription of Scn2a gene, but after knocking down FoxD3, the expression of Scn2a gene could increase, reducing the damage of magnesium free extracellular fluid to neurons in the refractory epilepsy cell model [8].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="本研究便是按此方法建立了难治性癫痫细胞模型，来进一步研究 SERCA 在难治性癫痫的发病机制中的作用及天麻素的药理作用。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="101">According to this method, the cell model of refractory epilepsy was established to further study the role of SERCA in the pathogenesis of refractory epilepsy and the pharmacological effect of gastrodin.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;line-height:150%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="在我们的实验中发现在模型组，凋亡指标c- PARP蛋白的表达明显上调（P＜0.01），存在明显的神经元凋亡；相比于对照组，模型组ATP2a2 （SERCA2）mRN A 出现表达量降低（P＜0.05），说明SERCA2参与了癫痫的发作以及神经元的凋亡。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="102">In our experiment, we found that in the model group, the expression of c-parp protein was significantly up-regulated (P.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="SERCA 是大小为 110 kDa的膜转运蛋白，能利用ATP水解释放的能量将 Ca2+从胞质转运到肌浆网（肌细胞）或内质网（非肌细胞）中储存，以维持细胞内钙浓度在静息状态的低水平（约 100 nM）[4, 9, 10]，是钙稳态维持中唯一能降低胞内钙水平的部分。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="103">SERCA is a membrane transporter of 110 kDa in size. It can transport Ca2 + from cytoplasm to sarcoplasmic reticulum (myocyte) or endoplasmic reticulum (non myocyte) by using the energy released by ATP hydrolysis, so as to maintain the low level of intracellular calcium concentration in resting state (about 100 nm) [4, 9, 10], which is the only part that can reduce the level of intracellular calcium in the maintenance of calcium homeostasis.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="SERCA2（ATP2a2），作为SERCA大家族中的一部分，也具有从胞质转运 Ca2+至肌浆网（肌细胞）或内质网（非肌细胞）的能力。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="104">SERCA2 (ATP2A2), as a part of SERCA family, also has the ability to transport Ca2 + from cytoplasm to sarcoplasmic reticulum (myocytes) or endoplasmic reticulum (non myocytes).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="在脊椎动物， SERCA主要有3种由同源基因（A TP2A1- 3）编码的3种异构体[11]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="105">In vertebrates, SERCA has three main isomers encoded by homologous gene (atp2a1-3) [11].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="无脊椎动物通常只表达 SERCA2，而脊椎动物有广泛表达的SERCA2b和选择性表达于骨骼肌、心肌、平滑肌及神经细胞的SERCA2a两种异构体[12, 13]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="106">In invertebrates, SERCA2 is usually expressed, whereas in vertebrates, serca2b is widely expressed and SERCA2a is selectively expressed in skeletal muscle, myocardium, smooth muscle and nerve cells [12, 13].</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="在我们的实验中也进一步发现，天麻素可以降低凋亡指标c-P ARP的表达（P＜0.05），同时100μM天麻素能显著上调ATP2a2（SERCA2）mRNA和蛋白质的表达（P＜0.05）。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="107">In our experiment, we also found that gastrodin can reduce the expression of C-P ARP (P &lt; 0.05), while 100 μ m gastrodin can significantly up regulate the expression of ATP2A2 (SERCA2) mRNA and protein (P &lt; 0.05).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="加入终浓度分别为 1μM、10μM、100μM、1 mM的天麻素，神经元状态有不同程度的好转，融合的神经元不同程度减少，神经网格分布比较均匀，100μM天麻素组（M+G）即更明显。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="108">When the final concentration of 1 μ m, 10 μ m, 100 μ m and 1 mm of gastrodin were added, the state of neurons was improved in different degrees, the fused neurons were reduced in different degrees, and the distribution of neural grid was more uniform, especially in the 100 μ m gastrodin group (M + G).</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="证实天麻素可以上调难治性癫痫细胞模型中降低的 SERCA2 水平，减轻无镁细胞外液处理对体外培养海马神经元的损伤。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="109">It is confirmed that gastrodin can up regulate the decreased SERCA2 level in the cell model of refractory epilepsy and reduce the damage of magnesium free extracellular fluid to cultured hippocampal neurons in vitro.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="已有研究发现天麻素[51]在各种模型中的不同生理效应[14]，如抗炎和抗氧化作用等。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="110">It has been found that gastrodin [51] has different physiological effects in various models [14], such as anti-inflammatory and antioxidant effects.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="钙超载、炎症和细胞凋亡在心肌缺血再灌注损伤（MIRI）中起到重要作用；Yufen Li 等[15]研究发现，SD 大鼠 MIRI 模型组 IL-6 和 IL-10 表达增高的同时，SERCA2 的表达降低了，而天麻素预处理可以上调 SERCA2a 表达，且呈明显的量-效关系，天麻素通过调控 SERCA 缓解钙超载而" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="111">Calcium overload, inflammation and apoptosis play an important role in myocardial ischemia-reperfusion injury (MIRI). Yufen Li et al. [15] found that the expression of SERCA2 decreased while the expression of IL-6 and IL-10 increased in Miri model group of SD rats, while the expression of SERCA2 was up-regulated by gastrodin pretreatment, which showed a significant dose-response relationship</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="减轻 SD 大鼠 MIRI 及炎症损伤。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="112">Reduce Miri and inflammatory damage in SD rats.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="天麻素还可以抑制体外原代培养的海马神经元及神经干细胞中β淀粉样蛋白导致的神经毒性[16, 17]；可以抑制鱼藤酮诱导的帕金森病模型大鼠的神经炎症[18]；还可以抑制缺氧诱导的原代培养大鼠皮层神经元的毒性[19]等。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="113">Gastrodin can also inhibit the neurotoxicity induced by β - amyloid protein in primary cultured hippocampal neurons and neural stem cells in vitro [16, 17]; it can also inhibit the neuroinflammation induced by rotenone in Parkinson's disease model rats [18]; it can also inhibit the toxicity induced by hypoxia in primary cultured cortical neurons in rats [19].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="关于天麻素抗癫痫作用的研究也多有报道，如通过抑制癫痫大鼠海马丙二醇（MDA）、增强其超氧化物歧化酶（SOD）及谷胱甘肽过氧化物酶（GSH-Px）活力，降低氧化应激水平而达到抗癫痫的效果[59]；通过降低戊四氮（PTZ）建立的癫痫大鼠模型p38MAPK 蛋白的表达及抑制 " class="translated-span" data-span-idx="114">There are also many reports about the antiepileptic effect of gastrodin, such as inhibiting the activity of MDA, SOD and GSH PX in hippocampus of epileptic rats, reducing the level of oxidative stress to achieve the antiepileptic effect [59]; reducing the expression and inhibition of p38MAPK protein in epileptic rat model established by pentylenetetrazol (PTZ)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="IL-1、IL-2 和 TNF-α等炎性因子的释放，影响炎症信号通路从而起到抗癫痫作用[20]。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="115">The release of inflammatory factors such as IL-1, IL-2 and TNF - α affects the inflammatory signaling pathway and thus plays an anti epileptic role [20].</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="因此我们推测天麻素抗癫痫及神经元凋亡还有其他的机制。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="116">Therefore, we speculate that there are other mechanisms of antiepileptic and neuronal apoptosis of gastrodin.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="从上所述，天麻素可以上调 ATP2a2 表达，将多余的 Ca2+转运至内质网，降低胞质钙浓度，改善钙超载，抑制异常放电神经元的兴奋性毒性，从而改善癫痫细胞模型中神经元的凋亡，达到抗癫痫的效果。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="117">From the above, gastrodin can up regulate the expression of ATP2A2, transport the excess Ca2 + to the endoplasmic reticulum, reduce the concentration of cytosolic calcium, improve the calcium overload, inhibit the excitotoxicity of abnormal firing neurons, so as to improve the apoptosis of neurons in the epileptic cell model and achieve the anti epileptic effect.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体" data-src-str="即天麻素可以通过上调ATP2a2 的表达来减少凋亡。" class="translated-span" data-span-idx="118">That is to say, gastrodin can reduce apoptosis by up regulating the expression of ATP2A2.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>

</div>